At all times of development, follow this tech stack:

**Frontend:** Next.js + TypeScript  
**Design:** TailwindCSS + Framer Motion  
**Auth:** Supabase Auth (GitHub + LinkedIn OAuth)  
**AI API:** User-supplied OpenAI API key  
**Storage:** Supabase (Postgres) or localStorage  
**Deployment:** Vercel  
**Rate Limiting / Queues:** Upstash Redis (optional)  
**Analytics:** Vercel Analytics or Google Analytics  
**Email (Optional):** Resend or Mailchimp (for onboarding, support)  
**Bot Protection:** ReCAPTCHA (if needed)  